{"tid":2410122,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟有一條巧，想申請攞打工皇帝呢個稱號。","createTime":"2021-02-16T10:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T07:17:19.000Z","uid":337498,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6adeff96c552e37ae2b9fa837e43cbcc1698fa4","tid":2410122,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"香港租貴，咁可唔可以唔租屋？但唔租樓訓邊？我認為，我可以考個保安牌，然後去返工廠大廈夜班，藉此訓覺。朝早就翻12個鍾救生員。咁即係一日24個鍾都有錢賺，而且兩份都係舒服工。<br />\n<br />\n老救70/h，保安50/h。半年為120*12*30*6=259200。而且無支出。食飯可以搵間包飯池做，例如D酒店池。<br />\n<br />\n冬天暫時未唸好做咩。或者可以去其它地方做保安。半年落來就100*12*30*6=216000<br />\n<br />\n成年計落淨收入近50萬。挨10年，一次過比錢買樓都仲得。如果識經營，借錢買幾層來放租，晚年無憂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我唔會咁做，一日返12個鍾泳池，我會癲。"},{"pid":"ff57b2eece4d3cf447e376b2ee7490659d77df2b","tid":2410122,"uid":113021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"你試一星期先講"},{"pid":"0170e1219f060095b446104e1a93cd863090b23d","tid":2410122,"uid":76053,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"24小時返工咁買樓有咩用"},{"pid":"c98ccc13deb139955ad11fcf7471ec4fff4bbd05","tid":2410122,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0170e1219f060095b446104e1a93cd863090b23d","tid":2410122,"uid":76053,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"24小時返工咁買樓有咩用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"星期日先返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9258bfe4d16035204a7446f2857aa2ffd27a0cd","tid":2410122,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:47:59.000Z","msg":"放假再做外賣師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偷食又唔洗比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f824bae01ffaae10637bc8c1b53d42eb60b1812","tid":2410122,"uid":166062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"事實上而家保安唔比訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （做緊）"},{"pid":"1a04a2fceaf78d8614cb4bfd2a40d4783703368f","tid":2410122,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c98ccc13deb139955ad11fcf7471ec4fff4bbd05","tid":2410122,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0170e1219f060095b446104e1a93cd863090b23d","tid":2410122,"uid":76053,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"24小時返工咁買樓有咩用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"星期日先返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"2份工都唔會放到星期日"}]}